            <title><![CDATA[Video: 11 Exciting New Games Coming To Switch 1 & 2 In June 2026]]></title>
            <link>https://www.nintendolife.com/news/2026/05/video-11-exciting-new-games-coming-to-switch-1-and-2-in-june-2026</link>
